# Coding-agent boilerplate manifest

This repository uses the standard coding-agent boilerplate.

Start here:

1. `AGENTS.md` - repository-wide instructions for coding agents.
2. `.agent/base-agent.md` - baseline operating prompt for autonomous coding agents.
3. `docs/AGENT-OPERATIONS-LOG.md` - append-only record of agent activity and handoffs.

When working in this repository, follow the nearest applicable `AGENTS.md` file and keep
the operations log current for meaningful setup, implementation, verification, and handoff
events.
